have names like ours.

81
00:06:57,320 --> 00:07:00,920
Noura, Shams, and Marzouqa.

82
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,200
You're so funny.

83
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:06,680
Alright, next time I'll check
the guests' names before I accept.

84
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,120
Good.

85
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:12,360
Is your leg any better?

86
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:17,960
Neither medicine nor treatment helped,
but thank God, I can still walk.

87
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:25,160
Here, this is for you and your family.

88
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:30,720
- Where did this come from?
- Quiet, don't let Shams know.

89
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:36,280
May God reward you and protect your family.
I don't know how to repay your kindness.

90
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,160
Hadeel, here you go.

91
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:45,200
Good work.
That's enough.

92
