the God of humankind

125
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:28,920
from the evil of the lurking whisperer who
whispers into the hearts of humankind

126
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:32,000
from among the jinn and humankind.
Allah has spoken the truth."

127
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:54,440
Peace be upon you. I'm Mishal,
a journalist from Al-Qabas newspaper.

128
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:56,240
