Thank you.

132
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,640
I'm the journalist Mishal Zayed.

133
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:35,720
- I'm sorry if I disturbed you, but...
- Get to the point.

134
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:43,480
Okay. Regarding your retirement,
there have been stories and rumors.

135
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:47,160
I read the investigation report,
and it was full of ambiguity.

136
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,480
What ambiguity?

137
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,160
About why you retired.

138
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:55,600
You were the most
famous folk singer in the Gulf.

139
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:59,240
You even overshadowed top singers.

140
00:13:00,400 --> 00:13:02,040
Are you ready to hear my story?

141
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:05,640
Yes.

142
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:11,360
If you insist on hearing the story,
the burden is yours to bear.

143
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:18,440
May I record?

144
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,640
Do as you wish, it doesn't matter.

145
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,920
